{
  "id": "RAW_ea3368",
  "title": "扣子空间上线极致拟人的 AI 播客，这次真是降维打击了。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647671466&idx=1&sn=b3d8c55ede560d4789e5b2e4bb3f164f",
  "date": "2025-05-28 01:03:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一篇文章，一键转成几乎跟真人无异的十几分钟中文AI播客。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有打断、有语气、有停顿，就特么离谱。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这，就是我用我现在的这篇文章，生成的AI播客。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-mpaudio class=\"js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card\" data-pluginname=\"insertaudio\" name=\"AI播客\" author=\"数字生命卡兹克\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=AI%E6%92%AD%E5%AE%A2&amp;play_length=\" isaac2=\"0\" low_size=\"3481.6\" source_size=\"3481.6\" high_size=\"3481.6\" play_length=\"299000\" data-trans_state=\"1\" data-verify_state=\"3\" duration=\"299\" voice_encode_fileid=\"MzIyMzA5NjEyMF8yNjQ3NjcxNDY1\" cover=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURqt1miauj0BZ5iaWpMatqMlgX2UBXg67yLkWfHZQpxmrb2pEw9fdgy1qibTvV7XCK7srxZI2uMaiaD1Rg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\"></mp-common-mpaudio>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个语气，这个聊天的感觉，我人麻了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个AI播客，来自于扣子空间。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">昨天，很多人在群里说，扣子空间的AI播客更新了，变得超级拟人。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bdfbc3ad-6917-425b-3258-094705fb4600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.34328358208955223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"536\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"536\" data-backh=\"184\" data-imgfileid=\"500187814\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bdfbc3ad-6917-425b-3258-094705fb4600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/095e397f-a6fd-4754-99c7-f0199cb85c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7197452229299363\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"628\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187815\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/095e397f-a6fd-4754-99c7-f0199cb85c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我就去直接试了一下。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当我实际听到扣子空间生成的AI播客音频的时候，我的第一反应是震撼，第二反应是恐惧，然后才是兴奋。</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-start=\"421\" data-end=\"453\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">震撼，是因为它生成的声音之真实、之流畅，让我几乎怀疑自己的耳朵。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"455\" data-end=\"495\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">恐惧，是因为这种效果似乎已经越过了某个阈值，打破了人机声音之间那道隐形的次元壁，我真的无法想象，我在听的东西，是AI生成的聊天。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"557\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">兴奋，是因为我知道，终于，这个世界上的无数内容创作者们，可以彻底摆脱过去声音内容生产的桎梏了，尽情享受一种前所未有的自由。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"557\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个AI播客，打开扣子空间（就是扣子做的那个Agent平台）就能直接使用。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"557\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">扣子空间网址在此：https://space.coze.cn/</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"557\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这里我插一句，扣子空间之前要邀请码，现在已经全量开放了，每个人都可以直接使用。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/570f0c96-05d1-4305-cd31-98293723ab00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5425925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187792\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/570f0c96-05d1-4305-cd31-98293723ab00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">想要做一个类似的AI播客，非常简单。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你什么都不用管，把你想要转成播客的文件素材，上传或者发送过去，然后说一句Prompt：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">“根据____，生成____分钟的双人播客，然后输出一个音频文件。”</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就完成了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不需要添加MCP，不需要引用任何插件，直接说一句话。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我前天写了一篇豆包视频通话的文章，大家反馈非常好，点赞啥的也很高。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/309f99e0-4fe6-4d57-3d86-46c7ff34db00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11145510835913312\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"969\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187794\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/309f99e0-4fe6-4d57-3d86-46c7ff34db00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是有朋友跟我说，文章明明写的很感动，但是她在早上开车的时候听，听AI念稿，还是很出戏的。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们就可以直接把那篇文章的地址从公众号里复制下来，然后跟着Prompt一起发送给扣子空间。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bb7de334-78f4-48e7-6869-fdecba25a500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5287958115183246\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"955\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187797\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bb7de334-78f4-48e7-6869-fdecba25a500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很快啊，它就会用一个网页读取的MCP，直接把我的所有文字扒下来。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4d943b12-7eb8-4ca6-b8e5-d3cbbd7ca700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5425925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187796\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4d943b12-7eb8-4ca6-b8e5-d3cbbd7ca700/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，大概几分钟，一个播客，就给我生成完了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5143c11a-920d-4b32-17fc-af9ecd3a9100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187798\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5143c11a-920d-4b32-17fc-af9ecd3a9100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你可以直接点击链接进行下载，大家可以听一听这个效果。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-mpaudio class=\"js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card\" data-pluginname=\"insertaudio\" name=\"扣子空间AI播客&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;卡兹克&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;豆包视频\" author=\"数字生命卡兹克\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=%E6%89%A3%E5%AD%90%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4AI%E6%92%AD%E5%AE%A2%26nbsp%3B-%26nbsp%3B%E5%8D%A1%E5%85%B9%E5%85%8B%26nbsp%3B-%26nbsp%3B%E8%B1%86%E5%8C%85%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91&amp;play_length=\" isaac2=\"0\" low_size=\"2662.4\" source_size=\"2662.4\" high_size=\"2662.4\" play_length=\"227000\" data-trans_state=\"1\" data-verify_state=\"3\" duration=\"227\" voice_encode_fileid=\"MzIyMzA5NjEyMF8yNjQ3NjcxNDY0\" cover=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURqt1miauj0BZ5iaWpMatqMlgX2UBXg67yLkWfHZQpxmrb2pEw9fdgy1qibTvV7XCK7srxZI2uMaiaD1Rg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\"></mp-common-mpaudio>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且最抽象的是，它不仅给我生成了播客，还预判了我的预判，给我写了一个网页。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c5db315-54da-4034-0fa0-5d0652db4b00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8009259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187803\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c5db315-54da-4034-0fa0-5d0652db4b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">https://space.coze.cn/s/94Zt6a9WO9Y/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">把播客，变成了可视化的播客，在这个网页上，不仅可以听音频，还能看到所有的字幕。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然NotebookLM前不久也支持了中文，但是坦诚的说，就是那个中文我是真的听不下去，听的我直皱眉头，太朗诵腔了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过扣子空间也有一个小问题，就是时长问题，我在Prompt里面明明说的是10分钟，但是我跑了起码5次，都是5分钟以内，直觉上是扣子的人因为算力，所以做了一些限制，要不然10分钟理论上应该没啥问题的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不知道大家怎么看AI播客这个事。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也不知道大家听不听播客，真的想做个调研，听过播客的举个手（可惜我看不到哈哈哈）。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说实话，我自己还是爱听的，因为确实有很多真知灼见，而且，是我为数不多的，能在内容形式上，感受到互动感和陪伴感的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有时候楼下溜达，或者在车上通勤的时候，我就会习惯性的打开播客，来听一集。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-start=\"619\" data-end=\"664\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过去，我们谈内容，大多都是文字或视频，这两种形式统治互联网这么多年，但它们各自有明显的缺陷。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"666\" data-end=\"758\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">文字虽然有深度、有效率，我也是靠文字为生，但坦诚的讲，文字这个东西天然缺乏情绪，读者的共鸣度除了笔力之外，其实大多数时候，完全取决于读者本人的代入感和想象力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"666\" data-end=\"758\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而视频虽然声画并茂，但创作成本极高，比如我的一期短视频，动效比较重，2分钟的视频我的剪辑几乎都要剪6个多小时，而且对于消费者来说，它几乎要消耗全部的注意力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"666\" data-end=\"758\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但播客不同，它只占用你最闲散、最被浪费的注意力，而不占用你必须投入的视觉通道，你甚至可以闭上眼睛，只需要倾听。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它本该是最平衡、最温暖、最有人情味的媒介，却一直处于一个尴尬的位置。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">人类主播的音频质量高但生产成本高昂，周期冗长，而传统TTS虽快速便宜，但是缺少互动感，特别是一些干货内容，TTS读出来的东西，我自己真的很难听下去。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像微信自带的这个听全文，我就想问你，当你在开车的时候来听我的文章，你是更想听一个冰冷冷的TTS呢，还是听一个类似于播客的形式，两人有来有回以聊天和讨论的方式，将其表达出来呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">答案不言自喻。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而AI播客，填补上了人类创作者数量不足的空白。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI播客不仅仅会成为内容的载体，我觉得也像可视化网页一样，可能演化成一种新的媒介。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如未来人们可能更愿意在开车、洗澡、做饭时听新闻，听小说，甚至听公众号文章，而非用眼睛去盯着屏幕。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI播客的普及，会逐渐模糊听觉和视觉内容的边界。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">内容不再是内容本身，而是一种，流动的状态。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">文字转AI播客、PDF转AI播客、音频转AI播客、视频转AI播客等等，实在太有意思了</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我们不想在上班的时候公然摸鱼吃瓜，那其实，就可以把一个吃瓜PDF，直接转成AI播客，两人聊，可比看文字，更有意思。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个PDF是我文章里的老演员了，AI生成的，但是很对瓜味。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9282f4a8-479c-4f35-9c7e-5d4200931600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2204234122042341\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"803\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187804\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9282f4a8-479c-4f35-9c7e-5d4200931600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">只需几分钟。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cd27a0ae-6373-4212-2088-1686c9a45700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26296296296296295\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187805\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cd27a0ae-6373-4212-2088-1686c9a45700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个比吃瓜文档更沉浸式吃瓜的AI播客，就完成了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">https://space.coze.cn/s/r2CZypIP6RQ/</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/298be3f9-f2b6-4644-49f5-cc009c531c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0359508041627248\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1057\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187809\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/298be3f9-f2b6-4644-49f5-cc009c531c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">推荐听，超好听，我自己听的，津津有味的。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">甚至不仅是文件，你还可以，扔一段B站视频上去，让它给你生成AI播客+网页。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9c2e3f5a-2e80-4257-bdc1-647587f9f600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187807\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9c2e3f5a-2e80-4257-bdc1-647587f9f600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">https://space.coze.cn/s/5gMvrjjqjHI/</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且不止是扔一个文件上去，你其实提出一个问题，你让他搜索完以后跟你说，其实也没问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如最近闹得沸沸扬扬的特厨隋卞和MCN的事，大家肯定都知道了，然后有一个梗特别的火，叫i人团队。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果你没听过这个梗，不知道的话，其实完全可以跟扣子空间说一句：</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2027c70c-b8e2-47f7-af70-558b31b44500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.527114967462039\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"922\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187806\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2027c70c-b8e2-47f7-af70-558b31b44500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">无需文件，无需素材，直接一句话，他就会去搜索，搜索完然后给你生成，AI播客，让你最快速最生动最沉浸式的看懂，i人团队这是什么梗。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">https://space.coze.cn/s/arJLN3JEbbA/</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500187808\" data-ratio=\"1.0302114803625377\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3505c8c1-3d7e-43dd-ec68-9cca5c032600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"993\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3505c8c1-3d7e-43dd-ec68-9cca5c032600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后我想聊聊替代。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">诚然，很多人也在讨论，AI播客会不会对真人播客产生冲击。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我觉得，这个问题是对所有内容创作者都是一样的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">我依然认为，人类播客的独特吸引力仍不可替代。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真人主播通过长时间陪伴，与听众建立的是一种拟社交关系，听众喜欢的是主播鲜明的个性、真实的情感交流，这种由人性火花构筑的纽带并非AI一串流畅的话语能复制。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI播客可以提供知识和娱乐，但很难让听众对背后的AI人格产生认同和喜爱，因为大家都知道那不是真实的人。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以我觉得，其实扣子空间的这个AI播客，是把整个播客的盘子给扩大了，让更多人，理解、尝试播客的乐趣。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而不是替代。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">多个模态之间的相互流转，一定会是未来最主要的旋律。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">无需抵制，大胆去用就行了。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，我也还是觉得。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI播客很酷，很有趣，但是再有趣的场景，也不能替代真实的人际交流。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">毕竟，没有什么比和朋友面对面地聊天，一起分享观点和笑声更让人愉快的了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，最后。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你要不要一起找个时间，跟你的朋友，坐下来好好聊聊天啊？</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">说一句：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我请客，咱们边吃火锅边聊聊天，怎么样？”</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">wzglyay@virxact.com</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "扣子空间上线极致拟人的 AI 播客生成功能，可将文本、链接、视频快速转为双人对话式播客。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "扣子空间上线极致拟人的 AI 播客生成功能，可将文本、链接、视频快速转为双人对话式播客。",
  "summary": "文章评测并介绍了扣子空间最新上线的 AI 播客功能，该功能能够将文章、链接、PDF 甚至视频内容一键快速转换为高度拟人的双人对话式 AI 播客。作者体验后表达了震撼、恐惧和兴奋等强烈情感，认为其声音真实、流畅，“几乎跟真人无异”，打破了人机声音的次元壁。文章通过多个实际操作案例，展示了如何简单地通过上传素材或发送链接，并提供简单的指令（Prompt），即可生成带有字幕的可视化播客页面。作者认为这项技术极大地降低了音频内容生产门槛，填补了高质量人工播客生产成本高和传统 TTS 缺乏互动性的空白，可能演化为一种新的内容媒介形态，扩大播客的受众盘子。文章最后讨论了 AI 播客对真人播客的潜在影响，认为 AI 播客更多是拓展而非替代，因为真人主播建立了基于个性与情感的拟社交关系。文章指出当前存在生成时长限制的小问题。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "扣子空间 AI 播客的声音效果高度拟人，具有对话感",
      "explanation": "该功能生成的 AI 声音具备打断、语气和停顿，极大提升了声音的真实性和自然度，克服了传统 TTS 的生硬感。"
    },
    {
      "point": "内容素材来源广泛，操作流程极为简化",
      "explanation": "支持文章、链接、PDF、视频等多种输入形式，仅需简单 Prompt 即可生成，极大降低了内容生产门槛和技术使用难度。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 播客是新的媒介形态，拓展音频内容消费场景",
      "explanation": "相比文字和视频，播客占用注意力少，更适合通勤等场景，AI 播客普及有望模糊听觉与视觉边界，扩大播客整体市场。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "一篇文章，一键转成几乎跟真人无异的十几分钟中文 AI 播客。有打断、有语气、有停顿，就特么离谱。",
    "当我实际听到扣子空间生成的 AI 播客音频的时候，我的第一反应是震撼，第二反应是恐惧，然后才是兴奋。",
    "这个世界上的无数内容创作者们，可以彻底摆脱过去声音内容生产的桎梏了，尽情享受一种前所未有的自由。",
    "而 AI 播客，填补上了人类创作者数量不足的空白。",
    "我觉得，其实扣子空间的这个 AI 播客，是把整个播客的盘子给扩大了，让更多人，理解、尝试播客的乐趣。而不是替代。"
  ],
